data.description: Very popular plan from this Builder. Over 3,000 htd sq ft with 5 bedrooms/3.5 baths, and a 3rd garage. Composition concrete lap siding exterior with wood accents. 30 year architectural shingle on roof. Front and back covered porches. The interior is finished with LVP or hardwood, carpet, and tile. Plenty of trim. Soft-close cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances. Fans in all b'rms. Convenient butlers pantry is located between the formal dining-rm and the kitchen. Master suite with large shower on main floor. 4 more bedrooms upstairs plus 2 full bathrooms, as well as a central loft, bonus room and large storage area.Ravensbrook conveniently located between Whispering Pines and S Pines. .50 plus acre lots. Future pool and pool house. Sidewalks.
